public class WeightedAdjMatrixGraph<T>
extends WeightedAdjMatrixDiGraph<T>
implements NetworkADT<T>
An implementation of the GraphADT interface for a undirected graph using an adjacency matrix to indicate the presence/absence of edges connecting vertices in the graph.
